data.description: 4 beds/ 1 full bath and 1/2 bath with shower.  1,482 SQ FT.  Home and income opportunity goes with this four bedroom home on .57 acres of (C1B) commercial zoned property. Additional .375 acres and .1243 acres of (MA2) marine zoned property, totaling 1.0693 acres, with 135 feet of bulk headed waterfront, 200 foot pier, and 12  boat slips. Water depth from 4 to 10 feet, that can accommodate  boats in excess of 40 feet. Total income from 7 of the 12 slips in 2021 was $11,300. POTENTIAL $20,000 PLUS RENTAL INCOME IN ADDITION TO DRY STORAGE AVAILABLE.  Many upgrades and extras. Information sheet in the document section of the listing or may be emailed to interested parties.
